.000Z","msg":"用咗一段時期單反，<br />\n一換無反嗰下真係好用好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:47:07.000Z","msg":"點解嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:35:24.000Z","msg":"單反重，af比無反又冇大優勢，mf嘅話，ovf又冇peaking，對焦對到眼都朦<br />\n<br />\n然後evf可以即時preview個final product，wysiwyg，<br />\n影完唔太需要晒時間望多次張相，就算要睇都可以長望vf唔使望mon<br />\n低光又好望好多，影drama rehearsal嗰時可以全場show唔離開vf，<br />\n唔怕miss嘢<br />\n相反單反adjust完setting之後都係要影咗先知張相exposure成果，<br />\n而且ovf睇到嘅光影/色同cmos capture嘅又唔同，<br />\n即係影完都係要轉去望mon睇相，多幾個動作<br />\n<br />\n以前用單反真係好少用ovf影，多數睇mon，易adjust好多，<br />\n轉咗無反之後反而因為個mon太柒所以睇evf多好多<br />\n加上evf睇到嘅info比ovf多，個頭唔使郁嚟郁去，smooth好多<br />\n<br />\n最後一樣嘢就personal啲，就係冇戴眼鏡嗰陣用到evf但用唔到ovf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰時ocamp爛眼鏡，用ovf真係搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，雖然而家情況好咗好多，但無反食電點都多過單反<br />\n同埋ovf望落去個view係幾好J，好似中幅菲林機咁，<br />\n咁大個vf淨係望幾下都濕晒"},{"pid":"99d54e3af697421baa77de730832a84c361c63f0","tid":2440360,"uid":54655,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3b1278cdef92aa2ac335cfcf9822351cd85074c7","tid":2440360,"uid":386830,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2c9ae0735a642e1aea762096480eedcb1a76ce58","tid":2440360,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c41ecd4f0997552574fdb5aa9c4170a315ed68a3","tid":2440360,"uid":386830,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:04:54.000Z","msg":"用咗一段時期單反，<br />\n一換無反嗰下真係好用好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:47:07.000Z","msg":"點解嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:35:24.000Z","msg":"單反重，af比無反又冇大優勢，mf嘅話，ovf又冇peaking，對焦對到眼都朦<br />\n<br />\n然後evf可以即時preview個final product，wysiwyg，<br />\n影完唔太需要晒時間望多次張相，就算要睇都可以長望vf唔使望mon<br />\n低光又好望好多，影drama rehearsal嗰時可以全場show唔離開vf，<br />\n唔怕miss嘢<br />\n相反單反adjust完setting之後都係要影咗先知張相exposure成果，<br />\n而且ovf睇到嘅光影/色同cmos capture嘅又唔同，<br />\n即係影完都係要轉去望mon睇相，多幾個動作<br />\n<br />\n以前用單反真係好少用ovf影，多數睇mon，易adjust好多，<br />\n轉咗無反之後反而因為個mon太柒所以睇evf多好多<br />\n加上evf睇到嘅info比ovf多，個頭唔使郁嚟郁去，smooth好多<br />\n<br />\n最後一樣嘢就personal啲，就係冇戴眼鏡嗰陣用到evf但用唔到ovf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰時ocamp爛眼鏡，用ovf真係搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，雖然而家情況好咗好多，但無反食電點都多過單反<br />\n同埋ovf望落去個view係幾好J，好似中幅菲林機咁，<br />\n咁大個vf淨係望幾下都濕晒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T02:10:28.000Z","msg":"單反用mon真係會俾人笑<br />\n加上以前用mon會無左phase AF，得番濕尻contrast AF係度拉風箱<br />\n加上果陣EVF同依家完全兩個世界，所以一路屌左好耐無反上唔到大場面<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e89290efa151bb800c3acf792f1ed9b85c2a8a1","tid":2440360,"uid":296028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"99d54e3af697421baa77de730832a84c361c63f0","tid":2440360,"uid":54655,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3b1278cdef92aa2ac335cfcf9822351cd85074c7","tid":2440360,"uid":386830,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2c9ae0735a642e1aea762096480eedcb1a76ce58","tid":2440360,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:47:07.000Z","msg":"點解嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:35:24.000Z","msg":"單反重，af比無反又冇大優勢，mf嘅話，ovf又冇peaking，對焦對到眼都朦<br />\n<br />\n然後evf可以即時preview個final product，wysiwyg，<br /